
'''''Nairobi Half Life''''' ni film y'ikinamico yo muri Kenya yasohotse 2012 iyobowe na David "Tosh" Gitonga. Iyi filime yatoranijwe nka filime yo muri kenya yinjiye neza mu rurimi rw'amahanga muri Oscar  mu bihembo bya 85 bya Osama, ariko ntiyaboneka  k'urutonde rwa nyuma, kandi ni ubwa mbere Kenya itanga filime muri iki cyiciro. 

Mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya 33 rya Durban, Joseph Wairimu yatsindiye igihembo cy'umukinnyi mwiza.  Yatsindiye kandi igihembo cya Afurika Movie Academy igihembo cy'umukinnyi wizewe cyane kuva mu birori bya 9 . Yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi muri Afrika Magic Viewers Choice Awards 2014 .  

