== Kwakira ==
''Umunyamakuru wa Hollywood,'' Todd McCarthy, yashimye iyi filime nyuma yo kuyireba muri AFI Fest 2012: "Iyi kinamico  igaragaramo  ubunyangamugayo bufatika ."  KenyaBuzz yerekanye imikorere yibye yakozwe na Maina Olwenya ubwo Oti yagize ati: "Iyi mico ni ghetto kuruta kumva alubumu za kera za NWA. Avuga ko afite ubugizi bwa nabi kandi agenda nkaho atunze umujyi nubwo ari umugizi wa nabi. " 

Muri Werurwe 2014 Afurika Magic Viewers Choice Awards muri Werurwe 2014,  ''Nairobi Half Life'' yahawe ibihembo kuri:

* Umukinnyi wa Sinema mwiza (Christian Almesberger)
* Igishushanyo Cyiza cyo Kumurika (Mohamed Zain)
* Umuhanzi mwiza wo kwisiga (Elayne Okaya) na
* Umuyobozi mwiza wubuhanzi ( Barbara Minishi ).
